  <version>SUSE Rancher Prime: RKE2 (RKE2)</version>
  <descriptions treatment="append">
    <desc lang="en-us">
        <p>
          SUSE Rancher Prime: RKE2, also known as RKE Government, is SUSE’s
          next-generation Kubernetes distribution.
        </p>
        <p>
          It is a fully conformant Kubernetes distribution that focuses on
          security and compliance within the U.S. Federal Government sector. To
          meet these goals, SUSE Rancher Prime: RKE2 does provides defaults and
          configuration options that allow clusters to pass the CIS Kubernetes
          Benchmark v1.6 or v1.23 with minimal operator intervention. It alsoe
          nables FIPS 140-2 compliance and regularly scans components for CVEs
          using trivy in our build pipeline.
        </p>
      </desc>
  </descriptions>
